data.description: This spacious move-in ready home in South Gulf Cove is on a DOUBLE LOT and offers plenty of room for your family and friends.   This is a unique floor plan with dedicated roomy spaces for everyone to spread out. The kitchen boast granite counter tops, wood cabinetry and stainless appliances.  The chef of the family will appreciate its roominess when preparing meals. The master suite is large and has his & hers separate bathrooms offering convenience when getting ready for date night!  The secondary bedrooms have ample space and there is a flex/bonus room  with a closet that can be used as an office, den or gaming room! Enjoy the evening sunset with a cocktail from you screeded lanai. The home is freshly painted on the inside and has a brand-new roof.  The second lot has a shed for storage; there is room for your boat and all your toys! You could also use this extra space for a freestanding garage.  South Gulf Cove has a community boat ramp, a learning garden and several parks for your family to enjoy. You are just a short drive to the beautiful beaches of Boca Grande,  Historic Dearborn Street in Englewood or the festive nightlife of Englewood Beach! If you are a golfer you have found your paradise, there are plenty of courses within 15 minutes of this lovely home! Call today for your private showing. Don’t let this be the one that got away!
